description: This file defines a function to create an upload diagnostics object for the BBHM system, along with licensing and module information. It references a global header and provides an implementation for the function BbhmCreateUploadDiag.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE BbhmCreateUploadDiag(ANSC_HANDLE hContainerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hOwnerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hAnscReserved)
methods.description: Creates and returns a new upload diagnostics object handle for the BBHM system, by calling BbhmUploadCreate with provided context handles.
